\\u003eShuib\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"given-names\\\"\\u003eL.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"name\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"surname\\\"\\u003eYadegaridehkordi\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"given-names\\\"\\u003eE.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cyear\\u003e2019\\u003c/year\\u003e\\u003carticle-title\\u003eBig data adoption: State of the art and research challenges\\u003c/article-title\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"source\\\"\\u003eInformation Processing \\u0026amp; Management\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cvolume\\u003e56\\u003c/volume\\u003e\\u003cissue\\u003e6\\u003c/issue\\u003e\\u003cpub-id style=\\\"display:none;\\\"  pub-id-type=\\\"doi\\\"\\u003e10.1016/j.ipm.2019.102095\\u003c/pub-id\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e' href=\\\"#j_dim-2020-0005_ref_006_w2aab3b7c26b1b6b1ab2ab6Aa\\\"\\u003eBaig, Shuib, \\u0026amp; Yadegaridehkordi, 2019\\u003c/a\\u003e) platforms allows for the possibility of data-driven personas that are created algorithmically (\\u003ca data-toggle='tooltip'  ref-type=\\\"bibr\\\" data-tooltip-info='\\u003cspan class=\\\"ref\\\"  id=\\\"j_dim-2020-0005_ref_004_w2aab3b7c26b1b6b1ab2ab4Aa\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"mixed-citation\\\"\\u003eAn, J., Kwak, H., Salminen, J., Jung, S., \\u0026amp; Jansen, B. J. (2018). Imaginary people representing real numbers: Generating personas from online social media data. \\u003citalic\\u003eACM Transactions on the Web (TWEB)\\u003c/italic\\u003e, \\u003citalic\\u003e12\\u003c/italic\\u003e(4), 1\u201326.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"element-citation\\\"  publication-type=\\\"journal\\\" publication-format=\\\"print\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"name\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"surname\\\"\\u003eAn\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"given-names\\\"\\u003eJ.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"name\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"surname\\\"\\u003eKwak\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=