of data-driven personas amidst analytics use cases by examining specific use cases pertaining to digital marketing. This positioning is reflected in \\u003ca data-toggle='tooltip'  ref-type=\\\"fig\\\" rid=\\\"j_dim-2020-0005_fig_002_w2aab3b7c26b1b6b1ab1ab7Aa\\\"\\u003eFigure 2\\u003c/a\\u003e.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cfigure id=\\\"j_dim-2020-0005_fig_002_w2aab3b7c26b1b6b1ab1ab7Aa\\\" position=\\\"float\\\" fig-type=\\\"figure\\\"\\u003e\\u003ch2\\u003eFigure 2\\u003c/h2\\u003e\\u003cfigCaption\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003eConceptual positioning of the persona \u2013 analytics integration research.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003c/figCaption\\u003e\\u003cimg xmlns:xlink=\\\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\\\" xlink:href=\\\"graphic/j_dim-2020-0005_fig_002.jpg\\\" src=\\\"https://sciendo-parsed-data-feed.s3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/6005bbb5e797941b18f255fd/j_dim-2020-0005_fig_002.jpg?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\\u0026amp;X-Amz-Date=20211130T193832Z\\u0026amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host\\u0026amp;X-Amz-Expires=18000\\u0026amp;X-Amz-Credential=AKIA6AP2G7AKDOZOEZ7H%2F20211130%2Feu-central-1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\\u0026amp;X-Amz-Signature=e8d11230fb6383d9325ecf965b5bea4816a342f5e9829b6d8956461124844bd1\\\" class=\\\"mw-100\\\"\\u003e\\u003c/img\\u003e\\u003c/figure\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003eWhile there have been attempts to \u201cmodernize\u201d personas by automating their creation and tying the concept to behavioral online analytics data (\\u003ca data-toggle='tooltip'  ref-type=\\\"bibr\\\" data-tooltip-info='\\u003cspan class=\\\"ref\\\"  id=\\\"j_dim-2020-0005_ref_021_w2aab3b7c26b1b6b1ab2ac21Aa\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"mixed-citation\\\"\\u003eHammou, B. A., Lahcen, A. A., \\u0026amp; Mouline, S. (2020). Towards a real-time processing framework based on improved distributed recurrent neural network variants with fastText for social big data analytics. \\u003citalic\\u003eInformation Processing \\u0026amp; Management, 57\\u003c/italic\\u003e(1). doi:\\u003cpub-id style=\\\"display:none