572\\u003c/pub-id\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e' href=\\\"#j_dim-2020-0005_ref_020_w2aab3b7c26b1b6b1ab2ac20Aa\\\"\\u003eFriess, 2012\\u003c/a\\u003e) the end user\u2019s cognitive load (\\u003ca data-toggle='tooltip'  ref-type=\\\"bibr\\\" data-tooltip-info='\\u003cspan class=\\\"ref\\\"  id=\\\"j_dim-2020-0005_ref_068_w2aab3b7c26b1b6b1ab2ac68Aa\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"mixed-citation\\\"\\u003eSweller, J. (1988). Cognitive load during problem solving: Effects on learning. \\u003citalic\\u003eCognitive Science\\u003c/italic\\u003e, \\u003citalic\\u003e12\\u003c/italic\\u003e(2), 257\u2013285.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"element-citation\\\"  publication-type=\\\"journal\\\" publication-format=\\\"print\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"name\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"surname\\\"\\u003eSweller\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"given-names\\\"\\u003eJ.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cyear\\u003e1988\\u003c/year\\u003e\\u003carticle-title\\u003eCognitive load during problem solving: Effects on learning\\u003c/article-title\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"source\\\"\\u003eCognitive Science\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cvolume\\u003e12\\u003c/volume\\u003e\\u003cissue\\u003e2\\u003c/issue\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"fpage\\\"\\u003e257\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"lpage\\\"\\u003e285\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e' href=\\\"#j_dim-2020-0005_ref_068_w2aab3b7c26b1b6b1ab2ac68Aa\\\"\\u003eSweller, 1988\\u003c/a\\u003e). Personas \u201chumanize\u201d data by replacing numbers that most individuals struggle to memorize with people-based data representations that individuals naturally empathize with (\\u003ca data-toggle='tooltip'  ref-type=\\\"bibr\\\" data-tooltip-info='\\u003cspan class=\\\"ref\\\"  id=\\\"j_dim-2020-0005_ref_020_w2aab3b7c26b1b6b1ab2ac20Aa\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"mixed-citation\\\"\\u003eFriess, E. (2012). Personas and decision making in the design process: an ethnogra