_w2aab3b7c26b1b6b1ab2ac58Aa\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"mixed-citation\\\"\\u003eSalminen, J., Jansen, B. J., An, J., Kwak, H., \\u0026amp; Jung, S. G. (2018). Are personas done? Evaluating their usefulness in the age of digital analytics. \\u003citalic\\u003ePersona Studies\\u003c/italic\\u003e, \\u003citalic\\u003e4\\u003c/italic\\u003e(2), 47\u201365.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"element-citation\\\"  publication-type=\\\"journal\\\" publication-format=\\\"print\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"name\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"surname\\\"\\u003eSalminen\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"given-names\\\"\\u003eJ.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"name\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"surname\\\"\\u003eJansen\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"given-names\\\"\\u003eB. J.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"name\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"surname\\\"\\u003eAn\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"given-names\\\"\\u003eJ.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"name\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"surname\\\"\\u003eKwak\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"given-names\\\"\\u003eH.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"name\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"surname\\\"\\u003eJung\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"given-names\\\"\\u003eS. G.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cyear\\u003e2018\\u003c/year\\u003e\\u003carticle-title\\u003eAre personas done? Evaluating their usefulness in the age of digital analytics\\u003c/article-title\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"source\\\"\\u003ePersona Studies\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cvolume\\u003e4\\u003c/volume\\u003e\\u003cissue\\u003e2\\u003c/issue\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"fpage\\\"\\u003e47\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"lpage\\\"\\u003e65\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e' href=\\\"#j_dim-2020-0005_ref_058_w2aab3b7c26b1b6b1ab2ac58Aa\\\"\\u003eSalminen, Jansen, An, Kwak, \\u0026amp; Jung, 2018\\u003c/a\\u003e) (\\u003ca data-toggle='tooltip'  ref-type=\\\"fig\\\" rid=\\\"j_dim-2020-0005_fig_003_w2aab3b7c26b1b6b1ab1b1b3b3Aa\\\"\\u003eFigure 3\\u003c/a\\u003e for illustration). However, personalization is not the same as understanding the user. For example, a recommendation algorithm may personalize product suggestions for a given customer in such an effective manner that the user generally accepts the recommendation. However, this does not necessarily imply that the user is happy or pleased with the overall customer service.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cfigure id=\\\"j_dim-2020-0005_fig_003_w2aab3b7c26b1b6b1ab1b1b3b3Aa\\\" position=\\\"float\\\" fig-type=\\\"figure\\\"\\u003e\\u003ch2\\u003eFigure 3\\u003c/h2\\u003e\\u003cfigCaption\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003eAlgorithmic ad targeting and optimization (adapted from \\u003ca data-toggle='tooltip'  ref-type=\\\"bibr\\\" data-tooltip-info='\\u003cspan class=\\\"ref\\\"  id=\\\"j_dim-2020-0005_ref_064_w2aab3b7c26b1b6b1ab2ac64Aa\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"mixed-citation\\\"\\u003eSmith, S. (2015). \\u003citalic\\u003eThe Benefits of Machine Learning and Programmatic Buying\\u003c/italic\\u003e [Marketing]. Retrieved from \\u003curi\\u003ehttps://www.slideshare.net/Intelligent_Optimisations/the-benefits-of-machine-learning-and-programmatic-buying\\u003c/uri\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"element-citation\\\"  publication-type=\\\"web\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"name\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"surname\\\"\\u003eSmith\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"given-names\\\"\\u003eS.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cyear\\u003e2015\\u003c/year\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"source\\\"\\u003eThe Benefits of Machine Learning and Programmatic Buying\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"comment\\\"\\u003e[Marketing]. Retrieved from \\u003curi\\u003ehttps://www.slideshare.net/Intelligent_Optimisations/the-benefits-of-machine-learning-and-programmatic-buying\\u0