e\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"source\\\"\\u003eJournal of Marketing Research\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cvolume\\u003e45\\u003c/volume\\u003e\\u003cissue\\u003e1\\u003c/issue\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"fpage\\\"\\u003e60\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"lpage\\\"\\u003e76\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e' href=\\\"#j_dim-2020-0005_ref_005_w2aab3b7c26b1b6b1ab2ab5Aa\\\"\\u003eAnsari, Mela, \\u0026amp; Neslin, 2008\\u003c/a\\u003e). Knowing customer behavior in different channels is crucial for this activity (\\u003ca data-toggle='tooltip'  ref-type=\\\"bibr\\\" data-tooltip-info='\\u003cspan class=\\\"ref\\\"  id=\\\"j_dim-2020-0005_ref_024_w2aab3b7c26b1b6b1ab2ac24Aa\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"mixed-citation\\\"\\u003eJansen, B. J., \\u0026amp; Schuster, S. (2011). Bidding on the buying funnel for sponsored search and keyword advertising. \\u003citalic\\u003eJournal of Electronic Commerce Research\\u003c/italic\\u003e, \\u003citalic\\u003e12\\u003c/italic\\u003e(1), 1\u201318.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"element-citation\\\"  publication-type=\\\"journal\\\" publication-format=\\\"print\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"name\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"surname\\\"\\u003eJansen\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"given-names\\\"\\u003eB. J.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"name\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"surname\\\"\\u003eSchuster\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"given-names\\\"\\u003eS.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cyear\\u003e2011\\u003c/year\\u003e\\u003carticle-title\\u003eBidding on the buying funnel for sponsored search and keyword advertising\\u003c/article-title\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"source\\\"\\u003eJournal of Electronic Commerce Research\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cvolume\\u003e12\\u003c/volume\\u003e\\u003cissue\\u003e1\\u003c/issue\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"fpage\\\"\\u003e1\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"lpage\\\"\\u003e18\\u003c/span\\u003