onally created personas, most notably issues of data validity and practical value.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003eRelated works (\\u003ca data-toggle='tooltip'  ref-type=\\\"bibr\\\" data-tooltip-info='\\u003cspan class=\\\"ref\\\"  id=\\\"j_dim-2020-0005_ref_004_w2aab3b7c26b1b6b1ab2ab4Aa\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"mixed-citation\\\"\\u003eAn, J., Kwak, H., Salminen, J., Jung, S., \\u0026amp; Jansen, B. J. (2018). Imaginary people representing real numbers: Generating personas from online social media data. \\u003citalic\\u003eACM Transactions on the Web (TWEB)\\u003c/italic\\u003e, \\u003citalic\\u003e12\\u003c/italic\\u003e(4), 1\u201326.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"element-citation\\\"  publication-type=\\\"journal\\\" publication-format=\\\"print\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"name\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"surname\\\"\\u003eAn\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"given-names\\\"\\u003eJ.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"name\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"surname\\\"\\u003eKwak\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"given-names\\\"\\u003eH.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"name\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"surname\\\"\\u003eSalminen\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"given-names\\\"\\u003eJ.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"name\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"surname\\\"\\u003eJung\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"given-names\\\"\\u003eS.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"name\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"surname\\\"\\u003eJansen\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"given-names\\\"\\u003eB. J.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cyear\\u003e2018\\u003c/year\\u003e\\u003carticle-title\\u003eImaginary people representing real numbers: Generating personas from online social media data\\u003c/article-title\\u003e\\u003cspan class=\\\"source\\\"\\u003eACM Transactions on the Web (TWEB)\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u00