 the capabilities of the personas as an interface to full-stack systems present considerable promise for data-driven persona practices within the field of HCI and also offer considerable impact for decision-making in organizations that desire to understand their users.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003c/sec\\u003e\\u003c/div\\u003e\",\"keywords\":[{\"title\":\"Keywords\",\"language\":null,\"keywords\":[\"persona\",\"analytics\",\"data-driven personas\",\"data science\",\"conceptual analysis\"]}],\"recentIssues\":{\"10.2478/dim-2021-0011\":\"\\u003carticle-title\\u003eWhich Message? Which Channel? Which Customer? - Exploring Response Rates in Multi-Channel Marketing Using Short-Form Advertising\\u003c/article-title\\u003e\",\"10.2478/dim-2021-0012\":\"\\u003carticle-title\\u003eAn Effective Digital Safeguarding System in University Libraries: A Model Plan\\u003c/article-title\\u003e\",\"10.2478/dim-2021-0015\":\"\\u003carticle-title\\u003eAssessing the Relationship Between Technostress and Knowledge Hiding\u2014A Moderated Mediation Model\\u003c/article-title\\u003e\",\"10.2478/dim-2021-0016\":\"\\u003carticle-title\\u003eSeven Important Theories in Information Management and Information System Empirical Research: A Systematic Review and Future Directions\\u003c/article-title\\u003e\",\"10.2478/dim-2021-0013\":\"\\u003carticle-title\\u003eThe Geopolitical and Socioeconomic Factors of Digitization in Vietnam: Technology Adoption in the Art and Cultural Sector During the Covid-19 Pandemic\\u003c/article-title\\u003e\"},\"supplement\":[],\"apaString\":null,\"mlaString\":null,\"harvardString\":null,\"chicagoString\":null,\"vancouverString\":null,\"citBIBUrl\":null,\"citRISUrl\":null,\"citENDNOTEUrl\":null},\"seriesKey\":null,\"chapters\":[],\"chapterData\":null,\"bookList\":{},\"bookListForBirkha\":{},\"bookCategories\":null,\"bookTitleGroup\":null,\"bookVolumes\":null,\"flyerUrl\":null,\"pressReleaseUrl\":null,\"citBIBUrl\":\"/article/download/cite/BIBTEXT?doi=10.2478/dim-2020-0005